description:
finra.org maintains an API that returns information (in json) about a particular bond.  The finra API takes a CUSIP such as 45505MJM9 and returns data about the bond.

Acceptance Criteria
Be specific about what you want in the solution here.

A simple javascript function:

() => getDataFromFinra (cusip) {
  // authentication
  //make request to finra api
  //return data as json object
}

I should be able to plug in my API Key and secret key into your function and have it work.
